Package org.presentation.swing

Class TimeslotSettings

java.lang.Object
org.presentation.swing.TimeslotSettings
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseSettings
public class TimeslotSettings extends Object implements BaseSettings
The TimeslotSettings class represents the settings for managing timeslots in the application. It provides methods for adding and deleting timeslots, as well as generating timetables. The class extends the BaseSettings class and implements various functionality related to timeslot management. Note: This class assumes that the necessary services and dependencies have been properly injected or made accessible through the GUI.app instance.
